---
import DiscoveryFlightCTA from "../../components/DiscoveryFlightCTA.astro";
import ContactUs from "../../components/ContactUs.astro";
import HomeLayout from "../../layouts/HomeLayout.astro";
import AircraftPropellerImage from "../../../public/img/new-to-flying/aircraft-propeller.webp";
import RedArrowFleetImage from "../../../public/img/new-to-flying/red-arrow-fleet.webp";
---

<HomeLayout>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header
    class="relative h-screen-3/4 bg-new-to-flying bg-cover bg-center bg-black flex flex-col items-center justify-center"
  >
    <!-- bg-overlay to darken -->
    <div class="absolute bg-black/50 w-full h-full z-0"></div>
    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="text-white text-center z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">New to Flying?</h1>
      <h2 class="text-3xl tracking-wide">
        Get to know what pilot training is all about
      </h2>
      <a href="#contactUs" class="btn-red">Visit the Academy</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Section 1 -->
  <section
    class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center lg:flex-row bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-200"
  >
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center lg:py-10">
      <img
        src="/img/new-to-flying/cessna-student.webp"
        alt="Jet flying through clouds"
        class="h-[400px] object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center py-10">
      <div class="max-w-2xl px-5 lg:px-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center tracking-tight">
          Flight Training Overview
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-800 tracking-wider">
          <p class="pt-10">
            Allow Red Arrow Flight Academy to guide you to becoming a pilot with
            our renowned flight training. Our program is meticulously designed
            to take aspiring pilots from the fundamentals to the heights of
            flight capability. Guided by our expert CFIs, you'll experience a
            blend of comprehensive ground school education and hands-on flying,
            ensuring a well-rounded understanding of the art and science of
            aviation.
          </p>
          <p class="pt-10">
            From the thrill of your first solo flight to mastering advanced
            maneuvers, our step-by-step program instills confidence, knowledge,
            and the skills necessary to fly safely and competently. We would
            love to be the ones to make your flight dream a reality. Email us or
            stop by if youâ€™re interested.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/flight-programs/training-courses" class="">
          <div class="btn-red my-10">Visit Red Arrow</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2 -->
  <section
    class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center lg:flex-row-reverse bg-gradient-to-br from-main-red to-red-900 text-white"
  >
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center lg:py-10">
      <img
        src="/img/new-to-flying/instrument-panel.webp"
        alt="Student passes checkride at Red Arrow Flight Academy"
        class="lg:mr-10"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center py-10">
      <div class="max-w-2xl px-5 lg:px-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center tracking-tight">
          It All Starts with Your PPL
        </h2>

        <div class="text-gray-100 tracking-wider">
          <p class="pt-10">
            Becoming a certified pilot with Red Arrow Flight Academy, like many
            other achievements, has a process. Here's a breakdown of the key
            stages in your path to obtaining a Private Pilot Certificate (PPL):
          </p>
          <ol class="pt-10 list-decimal pl-10 flex flex-col gap-2">
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold">Step: Enrollment</span> Kickstart your
              flight training by enrolling in our Private Pilot Program. Begin the
              process by filling out our application form and emailing the required
              documents to info@flyredarrow.com. For in-person enrollment, bring
              a photo ID (driver's license) and proof of citizenship (passport or
              birth certificate).
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold">Step: Paperwork and Flight Kit</span> Upon
              arriving at our office, our front desk team will assist you in completing
              additional paperwork and integrating you into our online system. You'll
              receive a flight kit, including a backpack with an online ground course
              and essential materials for your at-home training.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold">Step: Instructor Match</span> Once the
              paperwork is complete, we'll match you with an experienced CFI who
              will guide you through the remaining stages of the program. Your instructor
              will become your mentor, providing personalized instruction tailored
              to your learning style and pace.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold">Step: Ground School Education</span>
              Immerse yourself in our comprehensive ground school education. Learn
              the ins and outs of aviation, covering navigation, weather patterns,
              regulations, and more. This foundational knowledge is essential for
              a well-rounded understanding of flying
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold">Step: Hands-On Flight Training</span> Transition
              from the classroom to hands-on flight training. Experience the feeling
              of taking control of the aircraft under the guidance of your instructor.
              Master basic maneuvers and gain confidence in handling the aircraft.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold">Step: Solo Flight</span> Achieve a significant
              milestone by completing your first solo flight. This transformative
              experience marks your growing independence and proficiency as a pilot.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold">Step: FAA Written Exam</span> Complete
              the FAA written exam, demonstrating your theoretical understanding
              of aviation. Prepare with the guidance of your instructor to ensure
              success.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold">Step: Checkride</span> Undergo a checkride
              with a Red Arrow instructor. This test assesses your ability to apply
              theoretical knowledge and execute practical flying skills.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold"
                >Step 9: Private Pilot License (PPL)</span
              > Upon successful completion of the written exam and checkride, you'll
              be awarded your Private Pilot License. This certification opens doors
              to further advancements in your aviation journey.
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        <a href="/discovery-flight" class="">
          <div class="btn-black my-10">Book a Discovery Flight</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3 -->
  <section
    class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center lg:flex-row bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-200"
  >
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center lg:py-10">
      <img
        src="/img/new-to-flying/student-passes-checkride.webp"
        alt="Instrument panel of a Cessna aircraft over El Paso, TX"
        class="h-[500px] object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center py-10">
      <div class="max-w-2xl px-5 lg:px-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center tracking-tight">
          Flight Training Overview
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-800 tracking-wider">
          <p class="pt-10">
            Our training course offering extends well beyond the PPL. No matter
            where you're starting from, our courses cater to every aspiring
            aviator's needs. We offer a range of ratings, including Private
            Pilot, Instrument Rating, Commercial Pilot, and Certified Flight
            Instructor (CFI). Tailor your training to your goals, and let us
            guide you to success in the next evolution of your pilot journey.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/flight-programs/training-courses" class="">
          <div class="btn-red my-10">Our Training Programs</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4 -->
  <section
    class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center lg:flex-row-reverse bg-gradient-to-br from-main-red to-red-900 text-white"
  >
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center lg:py-10">
      <img
        src="/img/new-to-flying/aircraft-propeller.webp"
        alt="Propeller of an aircraft in black and white"
        class="h-[500px] object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center py-10">
      <div class="max-w-2xl px-5 lg:px-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center tracking-tight">
          Budget Considerations
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-100 tracking-wider">
          <p class="pt-10">
            As you embark on your aviation journey, understanding budget
            considerations is crucial. Red Arrow Flight Academy operates on a
            pay-as-you-go basis, eliminating the need for down payments or
            long-term contracts. Whether pursuing a Private Pilot License or
            advancing to a Commercial Pilot License, we would like to provide
            color as much as we can into what it can cost to engage in flight
            training. Please bear in mind that these are not always fixed prices
            as it takes some students longer than others to advance through
            training.
          </p>
          <p class="pt-10">Estimated Flight Training Costs:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-5 flex flex-col gap-1">
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold">Private Pilot License:</span> Estimated
              $12,000 to $18,000
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold"
                >Commercial Pilot License (with no prior experience):</span
              > Approximately $84,000 for Private Pilot License, Instrument Rating,
              and Commercial License
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold"
                >Commercial Pilot License (with PPL):</span
              > Estimated around $67,000 for Instrument and Commercial Ratings
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="pt-10">
            <span class="font-semibold">Financial Support:</span> As a Part 141 flight
            school, Red Arrow is uniquely positioned to accept those leveraging their
            Post-9/11 GI Bills. We also have partnerships with the COOL Program (open
            to Army/Air Force for financial sponsorship of up to $4,000) and Purdue
            Global Universities for students looking to pursue flight as a career.
            For other financing options, please take a look at our Financing page.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/resources/financing" class="">
          <div class="btn-black my-10">Financing Options</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5 -->
  <section
    class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center lg:flex-row bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-200"
  >
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center lg:py-10">
      <img
        src={RedArrowFleetImage.src}
        alt="Red Arrow fleet on the tarmac outside the schoolâ€™s hangar"
        class="h-[500px] object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center py-10">
      <div class="max-w-2xl px-5 lg:px-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-center tracking-tight">
          Pilot Career Paths
        </h2>
        <h3 class="pt-10 text-xl italic">
          If itâ€™s a career in flight youâ€™re after, then we stand ready at Red
          Arrow to take you to those heights. Beyond the attainment of your
          Private Pilot License, our training programs open doors to a multitude
          of exciting career possibilities.
        </h3>
        <div class="text-gray-800 tracking-wider">
          <p class="pt-10">
            <span class="font-semibold">Commercial Pilot:</span> Elevate your aviation
            career by pursuing a Commercial Pilot License. This certification gives
            you the skills and qualifications necessary to fly for compensation or
            hire. Whether you aspire to pilot commercial flights, work for airlines,
            or engage in other commercial aviation roles, the Commercial Pilot License
            is your gateway to a dynamic and lucrative career.
          </p>
          <p class="pt-10">
            <span class="font-semibold">Flight Instructor:</span> Share your passion
            for aviation and become a Certified Flight Instructor (CFI). With this
            certification, you have the opportunity to guide and mentor new students
            on their journey to becoming pilots. Red Arrow Flight Academy values
            the importance of experienced instructors, and achieving your CFI opens
            the door to a fulfilling career in aviation education.
          </p>
          <p class="pt-10">
            <span class="font-semibold">Specializations in Aviation:</span> Our training
            programs lay the foundation for specialization in unique sectors of aviation.
            Whether you're interested in aerial surveying, aerial photography, or
            other specialized roles, Red Arrow Flight Academy equips you with the
            skills and certifications needed to excel in these distinct and exciting
            career paths.
          </p>
          <p class="pt-10">
            As you progress through our training programs, we are dedicated to
            providing you with the knowledge, hands-on experience, and
            certifications essential for pursuing your dream career.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/about/our-story" class="max-w-min">
          <div class="btn-red my-10">Why Red Arrow?</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action Banner -->
  <DiscoveryFlightCTA />

  <!-- Contact Us Form -->
  <ContactUs />
</HomeLayout>
